  <h2 id="level-requirements">Level-by-Level Requirements</h2>
  <p>Each JLPT level has specific requirements for vocabulary, kanji, and grammar. Understanding these benchmarks helps you set clear study goals and track your progress systematically. The table below shows the cumulative knowledge expected at each level.</p>

  <table>
